  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/OpenDirectory\/ODSessionProxyPassword\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T20:35:47Z\n---\n\n# ODSessionProxyPassword\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nThe password to connect with via proxy. The value is of type `NSString`.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet ODSessionProxyPassword: String\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **ODFrameworkErrorDomain**\n- **ODSessionProxyAddress**: The address to connect to via proxy. The value is of type `NSString`.\n- **ODSessionProxyPort**: The port to connect to via proxy. The value is of type `NSNumber`.\n- **ODSessionProxyUsername**: The username to connect with via proxy. The value is of type `NSString`.\n- **ODTrustTypeAnonymous**\n- **ODTrustTypeJoined**\n- **ODTrustTypeUsingCredentials**\n- **kODAttributeTypeAltSecurityIdentities**\n- **kODAttributeTypeHardwareUUID**\n- **kODAttributeTypeMetaAmbiguousName**\n- **kODAttributeTypeMetaAugmentedAttributes**\n- **kODAttributeTypeMetaRecordName**\n- **kODAttributeTypeNodeOptions**\n- **kODAttributeTypeNodeSASLRealm**\n- **kODAttributeTypeOperatingSystem**\n\n",
